
This list is still outdated.
Please report your experience and additions.

Mac OS X, MacPorts packages:
  ruby
  mysql5-devel
  rb-rubygems
  rb-mysql
  rb-dbi +dbd_mysql
  ImageMagick

Linux Packages, Ubuntu/Debian apt packages:
  ruby
  rubygems
  build-essentials
  mysql-server-5.0
  imagemagick
  libdbd-mysql-ruby
  libmagick9-dev

Rubygems (select newest version available, if prompted):
  mysql
  rack
  highline
  eventmachine
  daemons
  httpclient
  thin
  mkmf
  soap4r
  rmagick
  json

Locally, go to the himle server directory and run:
  pushd
  cd lib/util/randgen_c
  ruby extconf.rb
  popd

